689
01:03:13,760 --> 01:03:16,000
What is it to be nearer to something?

690
01:03:16,000 --> 01:03:19,199
Is it being a certain number of feet from something?

691
01:03:19,199 --> 01:03:25,439
And if I'm 10 feet from it, I'm nearer to it than if I'm 50 feet from it?

692
01:03:25,439 --> 01:03:26,000
No.

